ul.li:
UTF-8 BOM handling - specifies how to handle the Byte Order Mark (BOM) when saves an UTF-8 XML document:
Don't Write - do not save the BOM bytes. Loaded BOM bytes are ignored;
Write - save the BOM bytes;
Keep - do not alter the BOM declaration of the currently open file. This is the default option. The UTF-16 BOM is always preserved. UTF-32 documents have a big-endian byte order.
